{"cid": "UgyLAWSuaxPLWbayjIN4AaABAg", "text": "Dear Raghu,\n\nI watched the video you shared me and it’s a beautiful initiative you started in Dubai, and I felt deeply moved and inspired. Opening a café for your beloved son and creating opportunities for specially abled children, particularly those with Down syndrome, is not just a business idea it is a noble mission filled with compassion, dignity, and humanity.\n\nWhat you have done is truly remarkable. By training and employing these wonderful children, you are not only giving them work but also giving them confidence, independence, and a sense of belonging in society. This kind of initiative changes lives, not only for the children but also for their families who see hope and pride in their achievements.\n\nYour café stands as a shining example of how love for a child can grow into a powerful movement that uplifts many others. It takes a big heart, courage, and vision to turn such a dream into reality, and you have done it beautifully.\n\nMay the Almighty bless you, your son, and your entire family with endless strength, happiness, and success. \n\nMy heartfelt prayers are also for all the wonderful children working in your café may their lives be filled with confidence, dignity, joy, and bright opportunities ahead.\n\nMay your initiative continue to grow and inspire many more people around the world to create inclusive spaces where every child is valued and empowered.\n\nWith deepest respect and admiration. 🙏🙏🙏🫡🫡🫡\nSyed Hamid Hassan", "time": "há 3 meses", "author": "@hamidhassan567", "channel": "UCNYm4MpB348tanomizPQo0A", "votes": "1", "replies": "", "photo": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_l7FP2TOwRNP4v8WaZGpv3q0C_vhoRP5sHuHnbsdfVQtUz4=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "heart": false, "reply": false, "time_parsed": 1774111462.965617, "video_id": "i0f8Jdw_jGI", "channel_id": "NewMedia_Life"}
